history.description: Isesengura ryuzuye ry'imikorere y'ishoramari hamwe no gukurikirana ROI n'ubushishozi bwo gucunga portefeuille.

plans.description: Kurema no gucunga ibicuruzwa by'ishoramari hamwe n'imyumvire y'ingaruka, ibarura ry'ibyasubiwemo, n'iboneza ry'amategeko.
plans.title: Imigambi y'Ishoramari

base.description: Sisitemu yuzuye yo gucunga ubumenyi hamwe no gushakisha gushingiye kuri AI no kunoza ibintu.

applications.description: Subiramo kandi ugatunganya ibyifuzo bya "Menya Umukiriya wawe" (KYC) hamwe no kugenzura inyandiko, gusuzuma ingaruka, n'imigendekere yo kwemeza.
applications.title: Amasaba ya KYC

levels.description: Shiraho inzego zo kugenzura hamwe n'ibisabwa byahinduwe, imipaka, n'uburenganzira bwo kwinjira ku bwoko butandukanye bw'abakoresha.
levels.title: Urwego rw'Igenzura

tools.description: Ibikoresho byo kubungabunga sisitemu birimo kunoza ububiko bw'amakuru, gucunga cache, n'ibikoresho byo kwimukira.

extensions.description: Urubuga rw'ubucuruzi bwa elegitoronike n'amasoko ya digitale hamwe n'ibikoresho byuzuye by'abagurisha no kurinda abaguzi.
extensions.title: Ibisubizo by'Isoko

wallets.description: Ubuyobozi bw'umufuka mukuru w'urwego rw'ikigo hamwe n'umutekano w'iminyururu myinshi n'ihuza ry'ububiko bukonje.
wallets.title: Amafaranga y'Umutwe

library.description: Ubuyobozi bw'itangazamakuru buri hagati hamwe n'ububiko bw'ibicu, kunoza amashusho, n'ihuza rya CDN kugira ngo imikorere ibe myiza.
library.title: Isomero ry'Ibitangazamakuru

marketplace.description: Isoko rya NFT ry'umwuga hamwe n'ibikoresho byo gucapa, ubuyobozi bw'amafaranga y'uburenganzira, n'ubushobozi bw'amasoko y'amadeni.
marketplace.title: Isoko rya NFT

templates.description: Inyandikorugero z'imenyesha zihindurika hamwe no gutanga imiyoboro myinshi n'impinduka z'umuntu ku giti cye.
templates.title: Inyandikorwa z'Imenyesha

management.description: Gutunganya ibicuruzwa hagati no gucunga ku mabuga yose y'ubucuruzi n'ibyiciro by'umutungo.
management.title: Imicungire y'Ibicuruzwa

platform.description: Urubuga rw'ubucuruzi hagati y'abantu hamwe na serivisi za escrow, gukemura amakimbirane, n'inkunga y'inzira nyinshi zo kwishyura.
platform.title: Ivunjisha rya P2P

gateways.description: Shiraho kandi ukurikirane inzira zo kwishyura hamwe no kumenya uburiganya, kugenzura ubwubahirizi bw'amategeko, n'isesengura ry'imikorere.
gateways.title: Inzira z'Ubwishyu

methods.description: Cunga uburyo bwo kwishyura buhari harimo amakarita, kwimura amafaranga muri banki, imifuka ya digitale, n'ubwishyu bwa cryptocurrency.
methods.title: Uburyo bw'Ubwishyu

systems.description: Ubuyobozi bwuzuye bw'ibikorwa remezo byo kwishyura birimo inzira, uburyo, n'igenzura ry'ibyerekeye ibikorwa.
systems.title: Sisitemu z'Ubwishyu

extensions.description: Imyongero y'urubuga ihanitse itanga imikorere yihariye ku bucuruzi, isoko, n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi.
extensions.title: Imyongero

settings.description: Iboneza ry'urubuga ry'ibanze harimo ibimenyetso, ubuhanga bw'aho, politiki z'umutekano, n'ihindurwa ry'ibintu.
settings.title: Igenamiterere ry'Urubuga

tasks.description: Uburyo bwo gutegeka imirimo ikora ubwayo hamwe no gukurikirana akazi, gukemura kunanirwa, no kunoza imikorere.
tasks.title: Imirimo Yateganijwe

orders.description: Ubuyobozi bw'ibicuruzwa byo gucuruza ku buryo butaziguye hamwe no gukurikirana ibikorwa mu gihe nyacyo n'isesengura ry'ingaruka ku isoko.
orders.title: Ibicuruzwa bya Spot

platform.description: Urubuga rw'ubushake rwa staking hamwe n'imicungire ya validator, ikwirakwizwa ry'ibihembo, n'uburinda bwo gutema.
platform.title: Serivisi za Staking

administration.description: Itsinda ryuzuye ryo kuyobora sisitemu kugira ngo ushire imiterere y'urubuga, gukurikirana, n'ibikorwa byo kubungabunga.
administration.title: Sisitemu

announcements.description: Sisitemu yo gutangaza ku rubuga rwose hamwe no gutegura, kugana, n'ubushobozi bwo gukurikirana imikoranire.
announcements.title: Amatangazo ya Sisitemu

logs.description: Sisitemu yo kwandika hagati hamwe no gukurikirana mu gihe nyacyo, gukusanya inyandiko, n'ubushobozi bwo gushakisha buyobowe.
logs.title: Inyandiko za Sisitemu

updates.description: Kuvugurura sisitemu bikora ubwayo hamwe n'ubushobozi bwo gusubira inyuma, ibice by'umutekano, n'ubuyobozi bwo kohereza ibintu bishya.
updates.title: Ivugurura rya Sisitemu

management.description: Ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bwa token buzuye hamwe no gucapa, gutwika, n'ubushobozi bwo kuyobora.
management.title: Imicungire ya Token

extensions.description: Amabuga y'ubucuruzi y'umwuga hamwe n'ubwoko bw'ibicuruzwa byateye imbere, ibikoresho byo gusesengura isoko, n'ibikorwa by'urwego rw'ikigo.
extensions.title: Urubuga rw'Ubucuruzi

infrastructure.description: Ubuyobozi bw'urubuga rw'ubucuruzi harimo abatanga amashanyarazi, imiterere y'isoko, na sisitemu zo gutunganya ibicuruzwa.
infrastructure.title: Ibikorwa remezo by'Ubucuruzi

logs.description: Amateka y'ibyerekeye yuzuye hamwe no gutunganya birambuye, ubushobozi bwo kohereza hanze, n'inzira zo kugenzura.
logs.title: Inyandiko z'Ibyerekeye Amafaranga

management.description: Igenzura ryuzuye ry'ibyerekeye hamwe no kwandika birambuye, guhuza, n'ubushobozi bwo gucunga imikurire.
management.title: Imicungire y'Ibyerekeye Amafaranga

management.description: Imicungire yuzuye y'inzibacyuho y'abakoresha harimo iyandikisha, ikemezwa, gutanga uruhare, n'ibikoresho by'aho abakiriya baherereye kugira ngo bikoreshe muri rusange.
management.title: Abakoresha

tracking.description: Ubuyobozi bwa UTXO buyobowe hamwe n'isesengura ry'igishushanyo cy'ibyerekeye n'ibintu birinda ubuzima bwite.
tracking.title: Gukurikirana UTXO

management.description: Ubuyobozi bw'imifuka y'amafaranga menshi hamwe no gukurikirana umubare, igenzura ry'umutekano, n'ubuyobozi bw'inyibutso.
management.title: Imicungire y'Amafaranga

logs.description: Koresha ibisabwa byo gukuramo amafaranga hamwe no gukurikirana imiterere, imigendekere yo kwemeza, n'igenzura ry'ubwubahirizi.
logs.title: Inyandiko zo Gukura

management.description: Ubuyobozi bw'umutego wuzuye wo gukuramo amafaranga hamwe no gutunganya bikora ubwayo, gukumira uburiganya, n'igenzura ry'ubwubahirizi.
management.title: Imicungire y'Ikuramo

methods.description: Shiraho uburyo bwo gukuramo amafaranga harimo kwimura amafaranga muri banki, gukuramo cryptocurrency, n'abatunganya nzego eshatu.
methods.title: Uburyo bwo Gukura

trading.title: Ubucuruzi
trading.description: Injira ku mihanda y'ubucuruzi yuzuye hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ibishushanyo byamamaye, amakuru y'isoko mu gihe nyacyo, n'ubushobozi bwo gukora nk'abahanga mu byiciro byose by'umutungo.

spot.title: Ubucuruzi bwo Mu Cyanya
spot.description: Kora ibyo watumije ako kanya kugura no kugurisha ku giciro cy'isoko hamwe n'ubwoko bw'ibyo watumije byamamaye, ibishushanyo by'ubujyakuzimu, n'ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bw'abahanga.

binary.title: Amahitamo Abiri
binary.description: Kora ubucuruzi bw'amahitamo abiri hamwe n'isesengura rihanitse, ibikoresho byo gucunga ibyago, n'ingamba z'umwimerere ku ngamba zikenera igihe.

forex.title: Ivunjisha ry'Amafaranga Amahanga
forex.description: Injira ku masoko y'ivunjisha ry'amafaranga amahanga yose hamwe na MetaTrader 4/5, ibishushanyo byamamaye, n'ingamba z'urwego rw'ikigo.

p2p.title: Ivunjugurane Hagati y'Abantu ku Bantu
p2p.description: Kora ubucuruzi bwa kripto butegerezwa hagati y'abantu ku bantu hamwe n'umutekano w'escrow, uburyo bwo kwishyura butandukanye, n'ibiciro bihanitse.

portfolio.title: Umutungo
portfolio.description: Inyandiko zuzuye zo gucunga umutungo kugira ngo ukurikire ibintu, usesengure imikorere, kandi ucunge ibikoresho byawe by'amafaranga kuri mihanda yose.

wallet.title: Imicungire y'Umufuka
wallet.description: Umufuka ufite amafaranga menshi utegerezwa hamwe no gukurikirana umubare mu gihe nyacyo, amateka y'ibikorwa, n'ubushobozi bwo kubika/gukuramo butoshye.

transactions.title: Amateka y'Ibikorwa
transactions.description: Amakuru arambuye y'ibikorwa hamwe no gushungura byamamaye, ubushobozi bwo kohereza hanze, n'inzira zuzuye zo kugenzura ibikorwa byose by'amafaranga.

transfers.title: Kohereza
transfers.description: Serivisi zo kohereza imbere n'inyuma hamwe n'ibikorwa byo mu cyanya, amafaranga ahanitse, n'inkunga y'amafaranga menshi.

investments.title: Ishoramari
investments.description: Amahirwe y'ishoramari atandukanye hamwe n'isesengura ry'urwego rw'abahanga, ibikoresho byo gusuzuma ibyago, no gukurikirana imikorere mu byiciro byinshi by'umutungo.

plans.title: Gahunda z'Ishoramari
plans.description: Ingamba z'ishoramari zatoranijwe zifite ibisobanuro birambuye by'ingaruka, amakuru y'imikorere y'amateka, n'amabwiriza yoroshye kugira ngo uhuje n'intego zawe z'imari.

staking.title: Ibihembo bya Staking
staking.description: Injiza amafaranga adasaba imbaraga binyuze muri cryptocurrency staking hamwe n'igipimo cy'APY gihembereye, igihe cy'imfunganwa cyoroshye, n'ikwirakwizwa ry'ibihembo ryikora.

ico.title: Igurisha rya Token
ico.description: Kwinjira hakiri kare mu buryo bwemejwe bwa Initial Coin Offerings hamwe na raporo y'iperereza ryuzuye, isesengura rya tokenomics, hamwe no gukurikirana ishoramari.

marketplace.title: Isoko
marketplace.description: Shakisha amasoko y'umwimerere na fiziki yujuje ubuziranenge hamwe n'ibikorwa byizewe, abacuruzi bemejwe, n'uburinzi bw'abaguzi burambuye.

nft.title: Ububiko bwa NFT
nft.description: Menya, uremewo, kandi ucuruze ibintu bya digitale by'umwihariko mu isoko ryacu rya NFT ryatoranijwe rifite ubushobozi bw'amacyamunara n'ubwishyu bw'abaremba.

store.title: Ububiko
store.description: Isoko ry'umwimerere riranga ibicuruzwa bya digitale na fiziki hamwe n'ibikorwa by'ubwishyu byizewe, kohereza ku isi yose, n'uburinzi bw'abaguzi.

services.title: Serivisi
services.description: Serivisi z'umwuga n'ibikoresho byo kunoza ubunararibonye bwawe bwo gucuruza, harimo gahunda ya affiliate, ibikoresho byo kwigisha, n'ubufasha bwihariye.

affiliate.title: Gahunda ya Affiliate
affiliate.description: Koresha urusobe rwawe rw'abantu binyuze muri gahunda yacu ya affiliate yuzuye hamwe n'amahoro ahembereye, gukurikirana mu gihe nyacyo, n'ibikoresho byo kwamamaza.

support.title: Ikigo cy'Ubufasha
support.description: Ubufasha bw'abakiriya bw'umwuga hamwe n'imicungire ya ticket, ubushobozi bwo guhuza mu buryo butaziguye, hamwe n'imicungire yihariye y'abakonti kubakoresha premium.

faq.title: Ububiko bw'Ubumenyi
faq.description: Inyandiko zuzuye, amahugurwa, n'ibibazo bikunze kubazwa kugira ngo ugufashe kugera ku ntego kamere y'urubuga.

insights.title: Ubushishozi
insights.description: Isesengura ry'isoko ry'umwuga, ubushishozi bwo gucuruza, n'amakuru y'inganda bituruka ku itsinda ryacu ry'inzobere mu by'imari n'abashakashatsi b'isoko.
